lterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871371960,45974302,7045]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67128788]天天困困困[/uid] (2026-06-11 13:43):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大狼大  套定律还会轮到吗[/quote]<br/>你理解什么是套定律扩产嘛？你知不道要买和华为强关联的？", "lou": 3125, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 871371960, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781156693}, {"pid": 871373308, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 13:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871373132,45974302,7048]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64768439]霄宮[/uid] (2026-06-11 13:53):[/b]<br/><br/>省流：散户多的不拉[s:a2:鬼脸][/quote]<br/>跟这个没关系 其实最核心是华为相关。算了 不懂自己问AI吧", "lou": 3126, "content_length": 57, "reply_to": 871373132, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781157323}, {"pid": 871374968, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 14:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "微盘股已经到那种  反弹一点就要跑的地步了。太惨了", "lou": 3127, "content_length": 46, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781158186}, {"pid": 871375249, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 14:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871375146,45974302,7052]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=37585733]j74587458[/uid] (2026-06-11 14:11):[/b]<br/><br/>死翘翘了，随便了[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>嗯 就是那种很绝望的盘口表现。", "lou": 3128, "content_length": 33, "reply_to": 871375146, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781158330}, {"pid": 871375696, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 203, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 14:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871375421,45974302,7053]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41884297]砂锅丶[/uid] (2026-06-11 14:13):[/b]<br/><br/>真的很感谢狼大，大盘跌成这个样最近几天我都没亏钱，甚至小赚。前几天清了光更是妙手[/quote]<br/>所以我都说了 你们根本不懂下跌通道做票的含金量<br/>大家都涨的时候人均股神 你们随便吹 我也不出声<br/>下跌的时候你们就知道技术的含金量了<br/><br/>我还是喜欢普涨大涨的时候看你们吹牛X的样子", "lou": 3129, "content_length": 166, "reply_to": 871375421, "14": {"13": 5}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781158568}, {"pid": 871376608, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 92, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 14:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正指数级别你们不用担心<br/>黄线都没新低 怕什么鬼 里面都是绝望盘都没你们那么怕<br/>虽然他们可能已经没有心跳了", "lou": 3130, "content_length": 98, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781159020}, {"pid": 871377451, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 41, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 14:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871377038,45974302,7057]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62832396]太太OvO贴贴[/uid] (2026-06-11 14:27):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大能不能聊聊微盘股未来的走势？<br/>之前微盘股年化吊打所有指数，但是今年是不是就不行了？<br/>结构性行情抱团科技，微盘跌<br/>等真的走大四抱团红利，他也跌<br/>现在的成交量要远远大于前几年，虽然流动性太聚集了。按理说只要有流动性，微盘就该涨才对[/quote]<br/>阶段不同  现在是赛道拥挤 机构卡再抱团里面等出场的时候。谁得空在缩量到2.5WE的时候还花筹码去不确定的微盘股<br/>而且准备半年报  微盘股ST的几率比确定性抱团的几率大多了。", "lou": 3131, "content_length": 160, "reply_to": 871377038, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781159431}, {"pid": 871377708, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 14:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871377174,45974302,7058]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60608517]Jerowe[/uid] (2026-06-11 14:28):[/b]<br/><br/>因为套定律，现在强华为相关的核心在拔估值吗[/quote]<br/>。。。。算了 你看我前面说的国产扩产逻辑吧 不重复了", "lou": 3132, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 871377174, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781159552}, {"pid": 871377832, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-11 14:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871377072,45974302,7058]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649